sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as 客户端
    participant E as CDN/WAF/排队层
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant RL as 限流 Redis
    participant S as Go 秒杀接入服务
    participant IR as 库存 Redis
    participant MQ as RocketMQ

    C->>E: 进入活动页
    E-->>C: 静态页或排队页

    C->>E: 获取短期资格票
    E-->>C: seckill_token + path_id

    C->>G: POST 秒杀请求<br/>request_id + token
    G->>G: 本地连接/IP/路由限流
    G->>G: 验签、版本、用户、设备校验
    G->>RL: nonce 防重放与全局准入
    RL-->>G: ALLOWED

    G->>S: 转发已认证请求
    S->>S: 本地用户限流、在途并发、售罄标记
    S->>IR: 库存预占 Lua
    IR-->>S: RESERVED + reservation_id

    S->>MQ: 发送订单创建消息
    MQ-->>S: 发送成功
    S-->>G: QUEUED
    G-->>C: HTTP 202 + reservation_id
